org.opends.messages

Class RuntimeMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.messages.RuntimeMessages

  • public final class RuntimeMessages
extends Object
    This file contains localizable message descriptors having the resource name org.opends.messages.runtime. This file was generated automatically by the i18n-maven-plugin from the property file org/opends/messages/runtime.properties and it should not be manually edited.

        public static String resourceName()
        Returns the name of the resource associated with the messages contained in this class. The resource name may be used for obtaining named loggers, e.g. using SLF4J's org.slf4j.LoggerFactory#getLogger(String name).

        The name of the resource associated with the messages contained in this class.
